{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "c3d4e5f6-a7b8-4c9d-0e1f-3456789012cd",
		"name": "BI-FAST Fraud Detection V3",
		"description": "End-to-end flow:\n\n1. Postman mengirim payload 23 field flat ke endpoint Elasticsearch `_ingest/pipeline/fraud_unsupervised_pipeline_v3_enriched/_simulate`.\n2. ES enrich processor lookup velocity aggregation per `sourceAccount` dari index snapshot `acct-velocity-snapshot` (di-update oleh continuous transform `acct_velocity_agg` dari index sumber `garda-context-bifast_trx`).\n3. Hasil enrich (amt_sum_2min/5min/1h/1d, tx_count_5min/1h, distinct_device/ip/location_5min) di-merge ke payload, lalu engineered feature di-generate (log_amount, fee_ratio, cross_bank, dst).\n4. Numeric scaling + one-hot encoding dijalankan via Painless script.\n5. Inference processor memanggil trained model `fraud_unsupervised_bifast_v3` (RandomForest surrogate dari IsolationForest).\n6. Band assignment script men-set `ml.is_anomaly`, `ml.outlier_score`, dan `ml.band` (LOW / MEDIUM / HIGH).\n\nThreshold:\n- MEDIUM = 0.6184259705500809\n- HIGH   = 0.7309104134367547\n\nAsal threshold:\nDikalibrasi saat training model v3 (lihat `models/model_meta_v3.json`). Skor mentah IsolationForest dinormalisasi min-max ke rentang [0,1]. Threshold dipilih dari distribusi skor 2006 transaksi training menggunakan metode `f1_max_vs_garda_rules` — yaitu memilih cutoff yang memaksimalkan F1 score terhadap label rule-based Garda. MEDIUM menandai ~10% transaksi paling anomali (201 dari 2006), HIGH menandai ~2% paling anomali (41 dari 2006).",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "basic",
		"basic": [
			{ "key": "username", "value": "{{esUser}}", "type": "string" },
			{ "key": "password", "value": "{{esPass}}", "type": "string" }
		]
	},
	"event": [
		{
			"listen": "prerequest",
			"script": {
				"type": "text/javascript",
				"exec": [
					"try {",
					"    const raw = pm.request.body && pm.request.body.raw;",
					"    if (!raw) return;",
					"    const resolved = pm.variables.replaceIn(raw);",
					"    const parsed = JSON.parse(resolved);",
					"    if (!parsed || !Array.isArray(parsed.docs)) return;",
					"    let mutated = false;",
					"    parsed.docs = parsed.docs.map(d => {",
					"        if (d && typeof d === 'object' && !d._source) {",
					"            mutated = true;",
					"            return { _source: d };",
					"        }",
					"        return d;",
					"    });",
					"    if (mutated) {",
					"        pm.request.body.raw = JSON.stringify(parsed);",
					"    }",
					"} catch (e) {",
					"    console.warn('pre-request wrap skipped:', e.message);",
					"}"
				]
			}
		},
		{
			"listen": "test",
			"script": {
				"type": "text/javascript",
				"exec": [
					"try {",
					"    const res = pm.response.json();",
					"    if (res.docs && Array.isArray(res.docs)) {",
					"        const cleaned = res.docs.map(d => d.doc._source);",
					"        console.log(JSON.stringify(cleaned, null, 2));",
					"        pm.visualizer.set('<pre>{{body}}</pre>', { body: JSON.stringify(cleaned, null, 2) });",
					"    }",
					"} catch (e) {",
					"    console.warn('post-response flatten skipped:', e.message);",
					"}"
				]
			}
		}
	],
